Q2. compose the commands fulfilled following requirement
i. count the no. of words ,characters and lines from above 2 file.(man wc)
ii. list the lines having word "files" (man grep)
iii. list the lines having word "file" (man grep)
iv. list the lines which don't have word "files" (man grep)
v. list the lines having word "have" . (man grep)
vi. list the lines starts with letter "f" (man grep)
vii. list the lines ends with "." (man grep)
viii. list only first two lines.(man head)
ix. list only last three lines.(man tail)
x. list line no.3,4 and 5 . (man head and tail)

Answer: 
i.  sunbeam@sunbeam-ASUS-TUF-Gaming-F15-FX506HF-FX506HF:~/CDAC/os$ wc sush1.txt
6  25 144 sush1.txt

ii.  sunbeam@sunbeam-ASUS-TUF-Gaming-F15-FX506HF-FX506HF:~/CDAC/os$ grep files sush1.txt
files have permissions.
files have inode no.
files have size.

iii. sunbeam@sunbeam-ASUS-TUF-Gaming-F15-FX506HF-FX506HF:~/CDAC/os$ grep files sush1.txt
files have permissions.
files have inode no.
files have size.

iv. sunbeam@sunbeam-ASUS-TUF-Gaming-F15-FX506HF-FX506HF:~/CDAC/os$ grep -v "files" sush1.txt
Linux is open source.
In Linux everything is file
there are several types of file

v. sunbeam@sunbeam-ASUS-TUF-Gaming-F15-FX506HF-FX506HF:~/CDAC/os$ grep "have" sush1.txt
files have permissions.
files have inode no.
files have size.

vi. sunbeam@sunbeam-ASUS-TUF-Gaming-F15-FX506HF-FX506HF:~/CDAC/os$ grep "^f" sush1.txt
files have permissions.
files have inode no.
files have size.

vii. sunbeam@sunbeam-ASUS-TUF-Gaming-F15-FX506HF-FX506HF:~/CDAC/os$ grep "\.$" sush1.txt
Linux is open source.
files have permissions.
files have inode no.
files have size.

viii. sunbeam@sunbeam-ASUS-TUF-Gaming-F15-FX506HF-FX506HF:~/CDAC/os$ head -2 sush1.txt
Linux is open source.
In Linux everything is file

ix. sunbeam@sunbeam-ASUS-TUF-Gaming-F15-FX506HF-FX506HF:~/CDAC/os$ tail -n 3 sush1.txt
files have inode no.
files have size.
there are several types of file

x. sunbeam@sunbeam-ASUS-TUF-Gaming-F15-FX506HF-FX506HF:~/CDAC/os$ head -n 5 sush1.txt | tail -n 3
files have permissions.
files have inode no.
files have size.

 













